reviewText: The Dvd is in a very good condition/ I am satisfied of the service of the Marinasbooks. Thanks a lot. Jeanne Goncharova.

I knew Vladimir Mashkov was a great actor, but I underestimated him. He is real David Gotsman.
The story itself is not too plausible, but is very interesting to watch anyway.

producer and actors created an unforgetting picture. the display of Zhukov is beliveable, the Mashkov is awesome, Oleg Basilashvili is unbelievable in short scene about psycologist. great work overall
